                  <EquationSource Format="MATHML">
                    <math xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">
                      <mfrac>
                        <mn>1</mn>
                        <mn>2</mn>
                      </mfrac>
                    </math>
                  </EquationSource>
                </InlineEquation> particle in a magnetic field <Emphasis Type="Italic">B</Emphasis>, with a negative scalar potential <Emphasis Type="Italic">V</Emphasis>, such that |<Emphasis Type="Italic">V</Emphasis>| grows at infinity. In particular, we obtain criteria for discrete and dense pure-point spectrum.</Para>
